title: Young Scooter - Cook Up Feat. Young Thug (Prod. By Zaytoven & Metro Boomin)
text:
0 MAKE IT STOP Young Scooter links up with Young Thug on the Metro Boomin and Zaytoven-produced "Cook Up." 
Freebandz affiliate Young Scooter is gearing up for a new mixtape. On Thursday, the ATL rapper dropped the single "Cook Up." Produced by superstar tag team Zaytoven and Metro Boomin and featuring Young Thug , this banger promises great things to come. 
Young Scooter spits that he's making an awful lot of dough and has all the gear to prove it. The producers wove several layers on this track creating a sort of wall of sound. Like everything Metro Boomin lays his fingers on, the spitters' bars work so well with the beat they blend in like extra musical instruments. By the way, Young Thug sings the magnetic hook and delivers a short verse near the end. 
Listen to "Cook Up" right here.
